	<h1 class="title">他把大麻做成这样，就想告诉你它没什么好大惊小怪的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-24 18:06:56 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22794/medium/22794.jpg?1456308381" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22794" data-title="《他把大麻做成这样，就想告诉你它没什么好大惊小怪的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22794/medium/22794.jpg?1456308381" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22794.html?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
